;serif&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 10pt; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast" lang="AR-SA">、</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;新細明體&quot;, &quot;serif&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 10pt; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast" lang="EN-US">dvd</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;新細明體&quot;, &quot;serif&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 10pt; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast" lang="AR-SA">：盜版、刮痕嚴重、缺歌詞或大陸</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;新細明體&quot;, &quot;serif&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 10pt; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-fareast-language: ZH-TW">版、</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;新細明體&quot;, &quot;serif&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 10pt; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast" lang="EN-US">vcd</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;新細明體&quot;, &quot;serif&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 10pt; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-fareast-language: ZH-TW">類不收</span></font></font></span></h1>\r\n<h1><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10pt"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;新細明體&quot;, &quot;serif&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 10pt; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-fareast-language: ZH-TW"></span></span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10pt"><font color="#808080"><font class="size_3"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;新細明體&quot;, &quot;serif&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 10pt; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast" lang="EN-US">11. </span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;新細明體&quot;, &quot;serif&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 10pt; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast" lang="AR-SA">高中、國中、國小等參考書及教科書</span></font></font></span></h1>\r\n<h1><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10pt"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;新細明體&quot;, &quot;serif&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 10pt; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast" lang="AR-SA"></span></span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10pt"><font color="#808080"><font class="size_3"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;新細明體&quot;, &quot;serif&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 10pt; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast" lang="EN-US">12. </span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;新細明體&quot;, &quot;serif&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 10pt; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast" lang="AR-SA">舉凡市場上過時、飽和、無法流通的</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;新細明體&quot;, &quot;serif&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 10pt; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-fareast-language: ZH-TW">書籍</span></font></font></span></h1>\r\n<h1><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10pt"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;新細明體&quot;, &quot;serif&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 10pt; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-fareast-language: ZH-TW"></span><font color="#808080"><font class="size_3"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;新細明體&quot;, &quot;serif&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 10pt; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast" lang="EN-US">13. </span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;新細明體&quot;, &quot;serif&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 10pt; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast" lang="AR-SA">其他：如影印、印『贈品』、盜版、缺頁、泡水、污漬嚴重的書</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;新細明體&quot;, &quot;serif&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 10pt; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-fareast-language: ZH-TW" lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></font></font></span></h1>', '', 2, '', 2, '', 2, '', '', 2, '', '', 2, '', '', 2, 'http://www.scsrc.org.tw/gs/', '我要捐書', 'http://', '', 'http://', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 0, '2012-03-15', '2012-04-03', 'adam'),
(67, 34, 3, '我要捐書', '', '', 0, '', 0, '', 0, '', '', 0, '', '', 0, '', '', 0, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'http://www.scsrc.org.tw/gs/', 0, '2012-03-15', '0000-00-00', 'pocheng'),
(68, 35, 1, '職業訓練中心願景', '<link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="content.css">\r\n<div class="header-image">\r\n<img src="t.jpg" alt="" class="img-full"></div>\r\n\r\n<div class="container">\r\n  <div class="content-text row-space-huge">\r\n     <div class="r">\r\n       <h1>脊髓損傷潛能發展中心 </h1>\r\n     </div>\r\n     <div class="r1">\r\n       <h1>附設職業訓練中心 </h1>\r\n     </div>\r\n  <div class="row row-space"><br>\r\n<br>\r\n\r\n    <p class="bodytext"><strong>設立主旨 </strong></p>\r\n    <p>結合職業訓練及就業服務政策，運用各項社會資源協助脊髓損傷者獲得就業之技能，進而回歸職場，達成企業與身心障礙者雙贏之目標。 </p><br>\r\n<br>\r\n\r\n    <p class="bodytext"><strong>職業訓練中心使命 </strong></p>\r\n    <p>協助身心障礙者培養一技之長，並輔導其就業，創造其職場價值。 <br>\r\n      <br>\r\n      培訓身心障礙者專業技能與職能，鼓勵終身學習，增進其職場競爭力與適應力。 </p><br>\r\n<br>\r\n\r\n    <p class="bodytext"><strong>職業訓練中心願景 </strong></p>\r\n    <p>104年前成為身心障礙者職業訓練之標竿訓練機構。 </p><br>\r\n<br>\r\n\r\n    <p class="bodytext"><strong>職業訓練中心核心價值 </strong></p>\r\n    <p>專業 <br>\r\n      <br>\r\n      同理 <br>\r\n      <br>\r\n      服務 </p> </div></div></div>\r\n', '', 2, '', 2, '', 2, '', '', 2, '', '', 2, '', '', 2, 'http://', '', 'http://', '', 'http://', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 0, '2012-05-08', '2017-09-25', ''),
(69, 36, 1, '愛心電子發票', '   <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="content.css">\r\n\r\n<body>\r\n<div class="header-image">\r\n<img src="donate.jpg" alt="" class="img-full"></div>\r\n\r\n<div class="container">\r\n  <div class="content-text row-space-huge">\r\n     <div class="r">\r\n    <h1>愛心電子發票</h1>\r\n      </div>\r\n  <div class="row row-space">\r\n    <font class="size_4">電子發票上路了,脊髓損傷潛能發展中心也有了自己的愛心碼,\r\n<b style="color:#4F2C0D; font-weight: bolder;">捐發票，愛地球；做愛心，更EASY。</b><br><br>\r\n\r\n現在只要結帳前告訴店員我們的愛心碼:\r\n<b style="color:#C10003;"><strong>518007</strong></b>\r\n或出示我們的:\r\n<b style="color:#C10003;"><strong>愛心條碼<img src="code.jpg" height="50"></strong></b>\r\n就可以將發票捐給脊髓損傷潛能發展中心\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>您的小小舉動 我們大大的溫馨</strong>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>脊髓損傷潛能發展中心由衷的感謝您<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n</strong></font>\r\n\r\n <p><font class="size_2">1.電子發票使用、捐贈方式及愛心條碼實施店家，依財政部公布為主，詳情請上</font><a href="https://www.einvoice.nat.gov.tw/wSite/mp?mp=1"><font class="size_2">財政部電子發票服務整合平台</font></a></p>\r\n   <p><font class="size_2">2.下載</font><a href="http://www.scsrc.org.tw/download.php?DB_FileTitle=%E8%84%8A%E9%AB%93%E6%90%8D%E5%82%B7%E6%84%9B%E5%BF%83%E7%A2%BC518007.pdf&amp;DB_FileName=13571816654.pdf"><font class="size_2">脊髓損傷潛能發展中心愛心碼<br></font></a></p>\r\n   </div></div></div>', '', 2, '', 2, '', 2, '', '', 2, '', '', 2, '', '', 2, 'http://', '', 'http://', '', 'http://', '', '脊髓損傷愛心碼518007.pdf', '13571816654.pdf', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 0, '2013-01-03', '2017-09-25', ''),
(70, 1, 1, '音樂會購票捐款', '<table cellspacing="1" cellpadding="2" border="0" style="width: 687px; height: 597px;">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td align="left" colspan="2">\r\n            <h3><span style="font-family: Verdana;"><span style="color: rgb(128, 0, 128);"><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><font class="size_5">感謝您支持『冬日暖陽 開創友善新世界』慈善音樂會活動</font></span></span></span></h3>\r\n            <span style="font-family: Verdana;">             <span style="color: rgb(128, 0, 128);"><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">                          <font class="size_5">             <span style="font-weight: bold;">                                       </span>             </font>                          </span></span>             </span>\r\n            <p><span style="font-family: Verdana;"><span style="color: rgb(128, 0, 128);"><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><font class="size_5"><span style="font-weight: bold;">您可以透過以下方式進行購票付款或贊助捐款</span></font></span></span></span></p>\r\n            <span style="font-family: Verdana;">             </span>\r\n            <p><span style="font-family: Verdana;"><font class="size_4"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 255);"><span style="font-weight: bold;">匯款</span></span></font></span></p>\r\n            <span style="font-family: Verdana;">             <font class="size_4">             </font>             </span>\r\n            <p><span style="font-family: Verdana;"><font class="size_4"><span style="font-weight: bold;">銀行 台新國際商業銀行 代碼 812</span></font></span></p>\r\n            <span style="font-family: Verdana;">             <font class="size_4">             </font>             </span>\r\n            <p><span style="font-family: Verdana;"><font class="size_4"><span style="font-weight: bold;">分行 營業部 代碼 0012</span></font></span></p>\r\n            <span style="font-family: Verdana;">             <font class="size_4">             </font>             </span>\r\n            <p><span style="font-family: Verdana;"><font class="size_4"><span style="font-weight: bold;">帳號 2001-10-0020759-2</span></font></span></p>\r\n            <span style="font-family: Verdana;">             </span>\r\n            <p><span style="font-family: Verdana;"><font class="size_4"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 255);"><span style="font-weight: bold;">郵政劃撥</span></span></font></span></p>\r\n            <span style="font-family: Verdana;">             </span>\r\n            <p><span style="font-family: Verdana;"><font class="size_4"><span style="font-weight: bold;">脊髓損傷潛能發展中心 19750664</span></font></span></p>\r\n            <p><br /></p>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td colspan="2" style="TEXT-ALIGN: left"><span style="FONT-SIZE: medium"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Verdana"><span style="font-weight: bold;">&nbsp;</span></span></span><br />\r\n            <table cellspacing="1" cellpadding="2" border="0" style="width: 544px; height: 63px;">\r\n                <tbody>\r\n                    \r\n                    <tr>\r\n                        <td align="left"><font class="size_3" face="Verdana"><img src="images/icon_g.gif" alt="" /> </font><span style="FONT-WEIGHT: bold"><a href="#" class="link_04"><font class="size_3"><font face="Verdana"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 255);">線上ATM付款</span><span style="color: rgb(255, 0, 0);">請點選此</span></font></font></a></span></td>\r\n                        <td align="left"><font class="size_3" face="Verdana">&nbsp;<span style="color: rgb(255, 255, 0);"><span style="background-color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="font-weight: bold;">捐款種類請勾選其他&rarr;備註音樂會購票</span></span></span></font></td>\r\n                    </tr>\r\n                </tbody>\r\n            </table>\r\n            <span style="FONT-SIZE: medium"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Verdana"><span style="font-weight: bold;"></span><br /></span></span><br /><span style="font-style: italic;"><span style="font-family: Verdana;"><font class="size_2"><span style="font-weight: bold;"><span style="color: rgb(255, 0, 0);">提醒您：捐款是可以抵稅的，而且每一筆捐款，本中心都會開立捐款收據。依所得稅法第十七條第一項第二款，捐款總額在綜合所得總額百分之二十以內將可列舉扣除。因此，您可將此捐款收據保存下來，隔年五月，申報個人所得稅時，憑此收據辦理減免稅金。<br /> 在此，也要提醒您，102年5月要申報要101年度的個人所得稅，是以101年1月1日至12月31日的所得為徵收內容。因此要利用捐款節稅的話，捐款日期必須是101年1月1日至12月31日這段期間的捐款收據&nbsp;，才能列入成為101年度扣抵所得稅的項目。</span></span></font></span></span><br /><br /><font class="size_3" face="Verdana"><span style="FONT-SIZE: medium"><span class="text_12px_04"><span style="FONT-SIZE: large"><span style="FONT-WEIGHT: bold"></span></span></span></span><span style="FONT-WEIGHT: bold"></span></font></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>', '', 2, '', 2, '', 2, '', '', 2, '', '', 2, '', '', 2, 'http://', '', 'http://', '', 'http://', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 0, '2013-10-15', '2016-08-31', 'admin');

